author: Derek Bayne
title: Lutheran volleyball clinches BNC West title
text:
Lutheran volleyball clinches BNC West title Posted: dbayne@wrex.com ROCKFORD (WREX) - 
Rockford Lutheran's volleyball team clinched an outright Big Northern West conference championship with a 2-1 win over second place Rock Falls Thursday night. 
Lutheran finished with one loss in the conference in Amanda Carlson's first year as the head coach. 
The high school volleyball playoffs start next week. Can't Find Something? 10322 Auburn Road, Rockford, IL 61103 Switchboard: 815-335-2213
